bitfield.doc:
UNK2 is supported by everything; SYNC only by QUERY/ZERO;
				     UNK0 only by QUERY/ZERO [unless UNIT is ZCULL], COUNTER/TRANSFORM_FEEDBACK,
				     COUNTER/GENERATED_PRIMITIVES, QUERY/STRMOUT_NO_OVERFLOW, QUERY/UNK03, QUERY/UNK04, QUERY/UNK0D. NFI what's the difference between UNK0 and UNK2.
